Welcome to Classilla!Classilla is the free, open-source Mozilla-based web browser for the classic Mac OS (8.6 and 9.x), offering improved support for modern web standards on your classic Power Macintosh system.Classilla is still under development. There are known bugs. Please read the online release notes at www.classilla.org for up-to-date information and complete installation instructions before you start using Classilla.Thanks for your support!Copyright 2009-2014 Contributors to Classilla. All rights reserved.